genresAdvancedInfo.name: chinese instrumental
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Chinese instrumental music is a genre that features traditional Chinese instruments such as the guzheng, erhu, and pipa. It often incorporates elements of Chinese folk music and classical music and is known for its delicate melodies and intricate arrangements.
